        You use instant messengers to chat with your friends or

        Encryption of popular instant messaging networks 

        SimpPro encrypts simultaneously text messages for the following
        IM networks: MSN Messenger, Yahoo! Messenger, ICQ, AIM, Jabber,
        Google Talk and most of their respective client applications.
        With SimpPro, chat securely with your business or personal
        contacts.


        Encrypted file transfers for MSN and ICQ/AIM 

        SimpPro transparently encrypts file transfers in MSN Messenger
        and ICQ/AIM. During a conversation, files sent are also
        automatically secured by SimpPro!
        For a comprehensive confidentiality,it is also possible to
        completely restrict unencrypted transfers. 


        Secured recording of conversations 

        SimpPro can optionally save conversations in encrypted form on
        your harddisk.
        Only the right key and passwords will give access to those
        records, which can then be directly displayed, sorted or exported
        to text format.
 

        Advanced cryptographic options 

        SimpPro offers you the strongest and most recent encryption
        algorithms, such as elliptic curves or 4096-bit RSA, 128-bit AES
        and more. It is also possible to disable specific algorithms or
        set priorities between them.

        SimpPro can be remotely deployed in a Windows domain using the
        remote installation service (RIS).

        SimpPro is now also fully compatible with the Microsoft PKI,
        simplifying both the end-user interface and the administrator's
        view of cryptographic certificates.
